    "description": "It's [[TibiaMaps]]' fansite item.  \n\nWhen using this item, a message related to one of the following 6 places will be displayed:\n# The alluring position is the {{Mapper Coords|text=small island|127.155|125.138|7|2|1|0.50.5}} in [[Jakundaf Desert]].\n# The captivating position is [[Sword of Fury]]'s {{Mapper Coords|text=small island|125.101|125.86|7|2|1|0.50.5}} near [[Rookgaard]].\n# The enthralling position is {{Mapper Coords|text=the island|126.62|124.193|7|2|1|0.50.5}} known as [[Isle of Solitude]].\n# The fascinating position is {{Mapper Coords|text=the island|125.163|126.47|7|2|1|0.50.5}} located West of the [[Adventurers' Guild]] known as [[Calcanea]].\n# The intriguing position is {{Mapper Coords|text=the unreachable ice island|125.248|123.101|7|2|1|0.50.5}} located Northeast of [[Senja]].\n# The mysterious position is {{Mapper Coords|text=the small cave|127.128|124.200|15|4|1|0.250.25}} where the NPC [[Basilisk]] is found.\n\nIt has also other stages that appear when interacted with:\n\n[[File:Armillary Sphere (TibiaMaps) 2.gif]]\n[[File:Armillary Sphere (TibiaMaps) 3.gif]]\n[[File:Armillary Sphere (TibiaMaps) 4.gif]]\n\nKnown players to have received this item are:\n\n* {{Character|Mathias Bynens}} as a contact person and member of the team.\n* {{Character|Robin Kint}} as the winner of the TibiaMaps.io fansite item contest (item creator).\n* {{Character|Hunter of Dragoes}}, {{Character|Lee kun}}, {{Character|Sofsterella}}, {{Character|Picture}} and {{Character|Spenceron}} for their contribution to the fansite.\n\nThis item was {{OfficialNewsArchive|6663|awarded}} to three players during the [[Fansite Appreciation Day 2022]]. The winners were:\n* {{Character|Lomer Zeth}} ([[Menera]])\n* {{Character|Kurayami'Dreed}} ([[Havera]])\n* {{Character|Tiu Lucca}} ([[Reinobra]])",
