    "description": "<br />\n==How to make Rum==\nTo make ''[[Rum]]'' [[File:Rum.gif]], you need...\n\n*[[Fire Bug]];\n*[[Sickle]] (or equivalent);\n*[[Distilling Machine]];\n*Any fluid container like [[Vial]]s or [[Mug]]s.\n\n# Use the fire bug on [[Sugar Cane]] to turn it into [[Burning Sugar Cane]] that will become [[Sugar Cane (Burnt)]] after the fire dies.\n# Use the sickle to cut it and leave [[Sugar Cane (Harvested)]] with a Bunch of Sugar Cane on top.\n# Pick up this bunch and use it on a [[Distilling Machine]].\n# Use the fluid container on the distilling machine to get the rum.\n\nNote: Each bunch of sugar cane provides 10 seconds of rum production.\n\n==How to make Sugar Oat==\nTo make ''[[Sugar Oat]]'' [[File:Sugar Oat.gif]], you need...\n\n*[[Sickle]]\n*[[Scythe]]\n*Bunch of Sugar Cane\n*[[Wheat]]\n*[[Fire Bug]]\n\n# Repeat the above process but instead of using your Bunch of Sugar Cane on a [[Distilling Machine]] use it on a [[Bunch of Wheat]].\n\nNote: You can use the [[Sugar Oat]]s on [[Wild Horse]] to get the [[War Horse]] mount.\nUse 50 of these on [[Distilling Machine]]s to obtain the [[Homebrewed]] [[achievement]].",
