    "description": "Cut wheat using a [[scythe]] and then use it with a [[millstone]] to make [[flour]], then use the [[flour]] with a bucket or trough of water to make [[dough]], then use the [[dough]] with an oven to make [[bread]]. Replacing the water with [[milk]], you get a [[cake]].\n\nTo make [[Sugar Oat]] {{Ilink|Sugar Oat}}, you need:\n\n* [[Sickle]]\n* [[Scythe]]\n* [[Bunch of Sugar Cane]]\n* [[Wheat]]\n* [[Fire Bug]]\n\n# Travel to [[Liberty bay]] and buy [[Fire Bug]]s from Evan {{Mapper Coords|126.3|128.113|7|3|text=here}}.\n# Go to the [[Sugar Cane]]s {{Mapper Coords|125.227|128.29|7|2|text=here}} and use the [[Fire Bug]]s to burn the [[Sugar Cane]]s down.\n# Pick up the Bunch of Sugar Canes and travel to [[Thais]] wheat field {{Mapper Coords|126.181|125.246|7|4|text=here}}.\n# Cut down the wheat with the [[Scythe]].\n# Use the Bunch of Wheat on the [[Bunch of Sugar Cane]].\n\nNote: You can use the [[Sugar Oat]]s on [[Wild Horse]] to get the [[War Horse]] mount.\n\n\nA lot of bunches of wheat can be found at daily spawns in one of the buildings in [[Rookgaard]], [http://tibia.wikia.com/wiki/Mapper?coords{{=}}125.83,125.185,7 here].<br>\nCut 200 of these to obtain the [[Happy Farmer]] [[achievement]].",
