    "flavorText": "It is nicely decorated with fruits, icing and a candle. Someone is caring about you.",
    "description": "Made with oven and [[Lump of Cake Dough]]. You can't eat it (you have to blow out the candle first).<br />\nIt looks the same as an [[Odd Hat]].\n<br />\n<table id=toc><tr><td align=left>\n'''How to make a Party Cake'''\nTo make a ''Party Cake'', you need...\n[[Flour]] (can be obtained by harvesting [[wheat]] in a millstone)<br />\n[[Milk]]<br />\n[[Oven]]<br />\nAny kind of [[Fruit]]<br />\n[[Knife (utensil)]]<br />\n[[Candlestick]]<br />\n1. Get the milk into a [[trough]] or [[bucket]].<br />\n2. Use flour with milk. You will get [[Lump of Cake Dough|cake dough]].<br />\n3. Use the cake dough with an oven. You will get a [[cake]].<br />\n4. Use the knife on a [[fruit]] (check table of fruits you may use [[Cooking#Fruits for Decorated Cake and Fruit Juice|here]]) while having the cake in your [[backpack]]. If you've done this correctly, there will now be red decorations on your cake, forming a [[Decorated Cake|decorated cake]].<br />\n5. Put the cake on a surface and drop a [[Candlestick]] onto it.<br />\nVoila! A perfect ''Party Cake''.</td></tr></table><br />\n{{clear}}\nBlow the candle out on 5 of these to obtain the [[Make a Wish]] [[achievement]].",
