    "description": "It heals 5000 [[HP]] instantly. Can be used 4 times.\n\nWhen using this item the first 3 times, the user will get the following message: \"{{Server Message|You take a gulp from the large bowl, but there's still some blackjack in it.}}\" At the fourth time, the user will get: \"{{Server Message|You take the last gulp from the large bowl. No leftovers!}}\" and the item disappears. [[Green Sparkles Effect]] {{Ilink|Green Sparkles Effect}} will always appear on the character that uses a Pot of Blackjack, regardless of whether it's the Pot's first, second, third, or fourth use.\n\nThe \"charges\" of this item are actually saved on the character as a counter, not on the item (as is the case with rings and amulets). This means that it is always safe to buy them from the market (and selling will not reset the charges), and it does not matter if you have more than one, because using either one will add to the character's count the same way.\n\nTo create this dish you must speak with the [[Djinn]] [[Jean Pierre]] in [[Ankrahmun]], near the Marid Fortress, during the [[Hot Cuisine Quest|Hot Cuisine]] event. The cooldown is shared with all other [[Jean Pierre]] dishes as well as with all [[Hireling]] dishes, but not with [[Cupcakes]].\n\n'''Necessary Ingredients:'''\n\n*5 [[Sandcrawler Shell]]s {{Ilink|Sandcrawler Shell}}\n*2 [[Vial]]s of [[Water (Liquid)|Water]] {{Ilink|Water}}\n*20 [[Carrot]]s {{Ilink|Carrot}}\n*10 [[Potato]]es {{Ilink|Potato}}\n*3 [[Jalapeo Pepper]]s {{Ilink|Jalapeo Pepper}}\n\nObtainable through the [[Hot Cuisine Quest]].",
