    "slug": "surprise-bag-red",
    "category": "Party Items",
    "type": "Party Items",
    "description": "Red Surprise Bags were added during [[Tibia's 10th Anniversary]], when they were rarely dropped by strong [[monsters]]. These bags contain rarer items than [[Surprise Bag (Blue)|Blue Surprise Bags]], but these in their turn contain some unique [[Party Items|festive items]].\n\nThe red surprise bag can contain festive items and rarer items. The following items are obtainable by using a bag:<br />\n{{Ilink|Fireworks Rocket}} [[Fireworks Rocket]]<br />\n{{Ilink|Cream Cake}} [[Cream Cake]]<br />\n{{Ilink|Bar of Chocolate}} [[Bar of Chocolate]]<br />\n{{Ilink|Party Hat}} [[Party Hat]]<br />\n{{Ilink|Piggy Bank}} [[Piggy Bank]] (semi-rare)<br />\n{{Ilink|Violet Gem}} [[Violet Gem]] (rare)<br />\n{{Ilink|Soul Orb}} [[Soul Orb]] (rare)<br />\n{{Ilink|Red Gem}} [[Red Gem]] (very rare)<br />\n{{Ilink|Teddy Bear}} [[Teddy Bear]] (very rare)<br />\n{{Ilink|Demon Shield}} [[Demon Shield]] (very rare)<br />\n{{Ilink|Panda Teddy}} [[Panda Teddy]] (very rare)<br />\n{{Ilink|Boots of Haste}} [[Boots of Haste]] (very rare)<br />\n{{Ilink|Dragon Scale Mail}} [[Dragon Scale Mail]] (very rare)<br />\n{{Ilink|Royal Helmet}} [[Royal Helmet]] (very rare)<br />\n{{Ilink|Amulet of Loss}} [[Amulet of Loss]] (very rare)<br />\n{{Ilink|Stuffed Dragon}} [[Stuffed Dragon]] (very rare)<br />\n\nDuring [[Tibia's 15th Anniversary]], the following approximate changes were made:<br />\n\n{{Ilink|Cream Cake}} [[Cream Cake]] &rarr; {{Ilink|Anniversary Cake}} [[Anniversary Cake]]<br />\n{{Ilink|Party Hat}} [[Party Hat]] &rarr; {{Ilink|Party Wall Snake}} [[Party Wall Snake]]<br />\n{{Ilink|Soul Orb}} [[Soul Orb]] &rarr; {{Ilink|Small Diamond}} 5 [[Small Diamond]]s<br />\n{{Ilink|Violet Gem}} [[Violet Gem]] &rarr; {{Ilink|Platinum Coin}} 15 [[Platinum Coin]]s<br />\n{{Ilink|Red Gem}} [[Red Gem]] &rarr; {{Ilink|Gold Ingot}} [[Gold Ingot]]\n\nBecause they bear similarity in probability, they may even share exact loot tables save for those item changes. The obtained items have now been reverted back and [[Violet Gem]]s for example can be obtained from 15th Anniversary Red Surprise Bags again.\n\nDuring [[Tibia's 10th Anniversary]], Red Surprise Bags may have also contained [[Red Balloons]].\n\n{{Seealso|Surprise Bag (Red)/Statistics|Surprise Bag (Blue)}}\n\nCan be obtained by [[skinning]] the [[Slain Mutated Pumpkin]] inside its reward room and by using [[Surprise Nest]]s. Could also be obtained from [[Anniversary Remains]] during [[Tibia's 15th Anniversary]].",
